_sText:
Well, I always loved bloorarena, so I thought it would be a good idea to remake this map with more futuristic effects. 
the map now has more strategic points, as there are now pahts. some glass walls have 200HP, some 1000HP, and some are unbreakable. HDR is also implemented. 
Special thanks to r00t666of666evil for hints and beta testing help.
